gujarati.context:
Infinite bliss of the formless, infinite joy from comprehension; 
Supreme bliss of non-physical forms, supreme joy from scriptural basis; 
Transcendent bliss beyond limits, eight-fold bliss of a great soul; 
Divine bliss of the sun-like one, unbound and liberal.

Joyful happiness, bliss of sight; 
Attention and meditation take hold; 
Divine joy, manly joy, knowledge and joy do.

The bliss of the creator is unbound bliss; 
the bliss of the spiritual guide is eternal bliss, 
unlimited bliss.
